posts.post_title: T206 Graded PSA SGC x 13 High Eye Appeal $SOLD
posts.post_content:
Well, due to some personal circumstances, I'm considering selling my mini-T206 graded card collection with awesome eye appeal. As you can see, many of the cards received lower than expected grade for reasons unknown

In terms of $, I'll take $SOLD (price added 10/27) and if I can't get it might break up into singles next week. 

Most of the backs are fine, a couple/few have tobacco staining. I do not think any of these cards have creases.  (Don't mind sending back scans to serious potential buyers.)

P.S. Thank you to board members who sold me a few of these cards as I appreciate enjoying them but may have to part with them (I did not buy them with the intention of resale but for personal reasons may release them).

PM me if interested....
